OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a mostly dry day,
OL,6,Falthough the morning will start with
OL,7,Flow cloud and some hill fog. Skies
OL,8,Fwill brighten with some warm sunshine
OL,9,Fbreaking through, although later in
OL,10,Fthe day cloud will increase again
OL,11,Fbringing patchy drizzle.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will be a cloudy evening
OL,14,Fwith some outbreaks of rain. The rain
OL,15,Fwill turn more patchy overnight.
OL,16,FFurther mist and fog patches
OL,17,Fdeveloping. Warm and humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
