OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FRather cloudy and misty
OL,6,Fwith patchy rain in the morning, this
OL,7,Fperhaps locally heavy in the south.
OL,8,FBrighter in the afternoon, though
OL,9,Fstill a chance of a shower.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FThe
OL,12,Fweather looks rather mixed to end the
OL,13,Fweek and start the weekend. Areas of
OL,14,Fcloud will give some rain at times,
OL,15,Fthough feeling warm in any brighter
OL,16,Fbreaks.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
